e earth,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "land, set barriers,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "obstacles, against him"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]; meaning,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "the ways became closed,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "stopped, against him, and the courses that he should pursue became obscure to him:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(K: in the CK"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Duribato", "text_ar": "ضُرِبَتْ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ":) the sing. of"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^asodaAdN", "text_ar": "اَسْدَادٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[accord. to general analogy] is"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "sud~N", "text_ar": "سُدٌّ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (TA.) ―         -b2-  [Hence,] the former ("}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "sad~N", "text_ar": "سَدٌّ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ") also signifies, (Fr, S, M, L, K,) or ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "sidaAdN", "text_ar": "سِدَادٌ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (A,) or the former and ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "sadaAdapN", "text_ar": "سَدَادَةٌ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (L,) (tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A fault,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "defect,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Fr, S, M, A, &c.,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "such as blindness"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "deafness"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "dumbness,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S,) or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "such as closes,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "stops, one's mouth, so that he does not speak:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(A:) pl. of the first, (S, M, K,) or of the second, (A,)"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^asid~apN", "text_ar": "اَسِدَّةٌ"}, {"kind": "