": "arabic", "text_bw": "sad~N", "text_ar": "سَدٌّ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "sud~a", "text_ar": "سُدَّ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ",] also signifies (assumed tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A she-camel by which the sportsman conceals himself from the game;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "also called"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "dariyoy^apNnd", "text_ar": "دَرِيْيَةٌند"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "dariyEapN", "text_ar": "دَرِيعَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "whence the saying,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "ramaAhu fiY sd~i naAqatihi", "text_ar": "رَمَاهُ فِى سدِّ نَاقَتِهِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(assumed tropical:)  ["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He shot him,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "shot at him, by his she-camel whereby he was concealing himself"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. (IAar, TA.) ―         -b5-  And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "sad~N", "text_ar": "سَدٌّ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (M,) or"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "sud~N", "text_ar": "سُدٌّ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (O, K,) is also"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "syn. with"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Zil~N", "text_ar": "ظِلٌّ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[as meaning (tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Shade,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "shadow;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "cover,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "protection"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. (IAar, M, O, K, TA.) A poet cited by IAar says,"}, {"kind": "quote", "text": "qaEadotu lahu fiY sad~i niqoDK muEaw~adK\n                      \n                     \n                        li*`lika fiY SaHoraA='a ji*omK dariynuhaA"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(tropical:)  ["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "I sat for him,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "i. e."}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "lay in 